-    allocations) and the compiled code is more compact and efficient.
-    For example
-
-    ```c++
-    #include <fmt/core.h>
-
-    int main() {
-      fmt::print("The answer is {answer}\n", fmt::arg("answer", 42));
-    }
-    ```
-
